Package: BiocPkgToolsPlus
Title: Analyse the Bioconductor Package Ecosystem
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2025-10-22
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Kevin", "Rue", "Christophe", "kevinrue@users.noreply.github.com",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3899-3872")))
Description: This package demonstrates use of BiocPkgTools functionality to
    study the composition the Bioconductor package ecosystem. This is meant
    to learn about packages, identify trends and issues in package annotations,
    and inform policies for package development and maintenance.
License: Artistic-2.0
